<div id="pf440c" class="pf w4f h2fe" data-page-no="440c"><div class="pc pc440c w4f h2fe"><div class="t m1500 x62 h49 y2e94 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 June 10-16 </div><div class="t m915 x15 h49 y2392 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord is not slack concerning </div><div class="t m13ad xb7 h49 y1584 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his promise, as some men count </div><div class="t m25 xb7 h49 y3 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">slackness; but is longsuffering to </div><div class="t m113b xb7 h49 y1586 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us-ward, not willing that any should </div><div class="t m55c xb7 h49 y60b ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perish, but that all should come to </div><div class="t m136b xb7 h49 yc45 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">repentance&quot; (2 Peter 3:9). </div><div class="t m6d5 x15 h35 y4c8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It has never been the plan of </div><div class="t me19 xb7 h35 yaa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God that sorrow, pain, and suffering </div><div class="t m6fb xb7 h35 y1ba4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should exist in the universe. When He </div><div class="t m978 xb7 h35 y349 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made man, He made him in His own </div><div class="t mdcb xb7 h35 y8e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">image. His eternal plan was that the </div><div class="t m6c7 xb7 h35 y52 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">more man lived, the more he would </div><div class="t m1d5 xb7 h35 y1cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reflect those divine characteristics </div><div class="t m594 xb7 h35 y5e3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that bring happiness, joy, and peace. </div><div class="t m7c8 xb7 h35 yaa4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But when sin entered into the picture, </div><div class="t m20e xb7 h35 y56 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the plans of heaven were temporarily </div><div class="t m832 xb7 h35 y5c3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disrupted, and the original intention </div><div class="t m1947 xb7 h35 ydc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God had to be postponed. </div><div class="t m355 x15 h35 yaa5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sin has spoiled the beauty and </div><div class="t m24c xb7 h35 y19f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">happiness the Lord wanted man to </div><div class="t m2a9 xb7 h35 yb7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enjoy from the very beginning. </div><div class="t m2e7 xb7 h35 y615 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nevertheless, God did not give up His </div><div class="t mf1d xb7 h35 yd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plan for a happy, holy human family. </div><div class="t m23d xb7 h35 ya58 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For this reason God will intervene in </div><div class="t m1113 xb7 h35 y159 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our world to destroy sorrow and sin. </div><div class="t ma33 x15 h35 y1d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We as the church of God are to </div><div class="t m882 xb7 h35 y452 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cooperate with Him in consummating </div><div class="t m228 xb7 h35 y65 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His wonderful agelong promises. If </div><div class="t m85a xb9 h35 yfc5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the individuals in the church had </div><div class="t m73e xb9 h35 y21b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trusted fully in Jesus and proclaimed </div><div class="t m1a4 xb9 h35 ya59 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the gospel of redemption to the </div><div class="t m58d xb7 h35 y134e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world, Jesus long ago could have </div><div class="t m449 xb9 h35 y2aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">brought the end of evil. And if we </div><div class="t m23d xb9 h35 yed7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are still in this world, it is because </div><div class="t m603 xb9 h35 y454 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we did not believe strongly enough to </div><div class="t mdec xb9 h35 y6f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cooperate with God in living and </div><div class="t mb0 xb9 h35 y37f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">witnessing. </div><div class="t m4a8 x27 h35 y325 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In spite of our past failure God&apos;s </div><div class="t m1a18 xb9 h35 y40f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work will be finished. There will </div><div class="t m3a9 xb9 h35 y166 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come an end to the agony of this </div><div class="t m730 xb9 h35 y1ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">planet of rebellious people. The only </div><div class="t m7d3 xb9 h35 y30a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reason why He seemingly delayed His </div><div class="t m789 xb9 h35 y344 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">supernatural intervention is not </div><div class="t m554 xb9 h35 yc9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">because He is &quot;slack concerning his </div><div class="t m2a9 xb9 h35 y884 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promise,&quot; but because He &quot;is </div><div class="t ma8c xb9 h35 y5e9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">longsuffering to us-ward, not willing </div><div class="t ma33 xb9 h35 y35c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that any should perish, but that all  </div><div class="t m5f6 x1c h35 y23e6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should come to repentance.&quot; On the </div><div class="t m1a4 x1c h35 y1584 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">other hand, the Spirit of the Lord </div><div class="t m232 x5a h35 y877 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;shall not always strive with man.&quot; </div><div class="t maed x56 h35 y385 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we will witness the </div><div class="t m233 x5a h35 y602 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">marvelous intervention of God and </div><div class="t m482 x5a h35 y32f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the final liberation of the saints at </div><div class="t m9da x5a h35 y61f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the time of the seventh plague. The </div><div class="t m156f x5a h35 y1ae4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day of doom and destruction for the </div><div class="t m114e x5a h35 y4bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">impenitent world, hardened in sin, </div><div class="t m2b9 x5a h35 y5cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be the day of joy and happiness </div><div class="t me69 x5a h35 y281 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the children of God, who for </div><div class="t mb9b x5a h35 y492 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such a long time suffered for their </div><div class="t m11c x5a h35 y242 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Master and endured the tempest of </div><div class="t mb12 x5a h35 y8a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecution but remained loyal. </div><div class="t mb5a x5a h49 y711 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m12c x5a h49 y454 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m7d5 x86 h49 y58c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Seventh Plague </div><div class="t m683 x86 h49 y25 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:17-21) </div><div class="t m814 x5a h49 y340 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m964 x86 h49 y84f ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">At the Hour of Utmost Extremity </div><div class="t m766 x86 h49 y294 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 37:40) </div><div class="t m66d x5a h49 y49c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m46d x86 h49 y49c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cataclysmic Events—I </div><div class="t m24f x4b h49 y166 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:17-21) </div><div class="t m7e1 x5a h49 y1ac ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m93f x86 h49 y42c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Sudden Change in the Scene </div><div class="t m1067 x4b h49 y1e5 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:17) </div><div class="t m2ef x5a h49 y344 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t maf9 x4b h49 y344 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cataclysmic Events—II </div><div class="t m42b x4b h49 yc49 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 76:7-9) </div><div class="t mb27 x5a h49 y885 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2fc x86 h49 y885 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Advent </div><div class="t m6e0 x86 h49 ya71 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 1:7; Jude 14, 15; </div><div class="t mafa x86 h49 y3b7 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 24:30, 31) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
